{
  "texts": [
    "Trained models can be deployed using the interactive interface on a variety of operating systems and hardware environments.",
    "Testing of this user interface has been performed on Linux-based systems, Windows, macOS (Intel and Apple chip), and ARM-based devices such as the Raspberry Pi and Jetson Nano.",
    "A dedicated GPU is recommended, but not required, for model deployment.",
    "Software development processesSlideflow has been engineered according to industry software quality standards.",
    "Source code adheres to PEP 8 style guidelines [72], supported through integrated pylint [73] checking."
  ]
}